@startuml Trip Creation Wizard Flow

!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontSize 12

title Trip Creation Wizard - User Flow

actor User
participant Dashboard
participant AddTripContainer
participant NewTripWizard
participant OverviewStep
participant "Other Steps\n(Placeholders)" as OtherSteps
participant TripService
database "In-Memory\nStorage" as Storage

User -> Dashboard: Views dashboard
Dashboard -> AddTripContainer: Renders "Add Trip" card
User -> AddTripContainer: Clicks card
AddTripContainer -> NewTripWizard: Navigate to /trips/new

NewTripWizard -> OverviewStep: Render step 1/6
User -> OverviewStep: Fills in:\n- Trip name\n- Destination\n- Start date\n- End date
User -> NewTripWizard: Clicks "Next"

NewTripWizard -> OtherSteps: Render steps 2-6\n(Flights, Stays, Activities,\nBudget, Team)
User -> OtherSteps: Views placeholders
User -> NewTripWizard: Clicks "Next" through steps

User -> NewTripWizard: On step 6, clicks "Save Trip"
NewTripWizard -> TripService: createTrip(formData)
TripService -> Storage: Store trip
Storage --> TripService: Trip created
TripService --> NewTripWizard: Success
NewTripWizard -> Dashboard: Navigate to /dashboard

Dashboard -> TripService: getAllTrips()
TripService -> Storage: Fetch all trips
Storage --> TripService: Return trips (including new one)
TripService --> Dashboard: Display trips
Dashboard -> User: Shows new trip in list

@enduml
